m'muz dokh aropgeyn epes zukhn, di ale sh- zek zenen gevorn farbrent, vu di esn, dos broyt vos m'hot gehat,

00:11:41.488 --> 00:11:44.351
s'nishto nisht keyn vaser, nisht keyn nisht keyn esn.

00:11:44.543 --> 00:11:47.290
iz men arop hintn arop fil veynik

00:11:47.290 --> 00:11:52.231
ho'mir undz nisht gevust vu SCHRONYn zenen do, vu vu bunkers zenen do.

00:11:52.525 --> 00:11:55.897
vayl ikh hob geven eyner vos ikh hob a mol geholfn frierdike

00:11:55.897 --> 00:12:00.484
geholfn a mol, ikh ho- ikh veys vi azoy m'hot ge- -boyen, nor ikh hob nisht gehat keyn UNK ⟨lebn mir⟩.

00:12:00.574 --> 00:12:05.051
ikh veys nisht far vos s'iz mir ayngefaln a meshugas nisht in di bunkers, UNK hob efsher moyre gehat

00:12:05.051 --> 00:12:11.402
az dos hoyz vert farshit mitn bunker. ikh bin geven aza moyre-hober tsu zayn farshit farmakht.

00:12:11.627 --> 00:12:16.396
hob ikh mir gevolt zayn fray. dos iz efsher geven mayn politik, azoy gloyb ikh.

00:12:16.825 --> 00:12:19.924
biz hayntikn tog afile, ikh hob nisht lib tsu zayn in keyn farmakhte,

00:12:20.402 --> 00:12:23.774
du farshteyst, azoy nakher, yo iz men arop in di

00:12:23.774 --> 00:12:29.508
fil veynik in UNK arayn, eyner fun di bunkers vos iz geven in Fratshishkana draysik, ikh gedenk far haynt,

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:40.646
un dortn zenen geven magazinen in der heykh, un hintn iz geven kelers vos zey hobn gehaltn leder, s'iz geven a leder gegnt. undzer gegnt iz geven UNK, der Frantshishkana iz geven in leder. leder ⟨brash⟩.

00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:43.127
iz men arop fun di arayn,

00:12:43.808 --> 00:12:48.577
un m'hot ongehoybn arayntsukrikhn, s'geven lekher arayntsukrikhn, UNK. m'iz arayngekumen dort

00:12:48.904 --> 00:12:53.319
a fintsternish, un m'iz gegangen mit di ⟨TORCH⟩, m'hot dokh gegat azelkhes

00:12:54.186 --> 00:12:58.061
m'hot gelornt, m'hot gezen nokh, s'ge- gedenk ikh vi haynt, iz gezitsn a froy,

00:12:58.489 --> 00:13:04.839
kimat vi blind far dem, s'geven fintster, un un zi hot nisht gekent shoyn nokh,

00:13:04.839 --> 00:13:12.050
m'hot geredt mit ir, zi hot epes geredt a por verter, zi iz geven azoy vi halb toyt, on esn, un m'geyt vayter,

00:13:12.124 --> 00:13:16.458
krikht men arayn in a frishn lokh. ikh veys nisht far vos di froy, tsi m'hot ir nisht arayngelozt,

00:13:16.458 --> 00:13:22.549
tsi zi hot shoyn nisht gekent arayngeyn, vos iz geshen mit ir, far vos zi iz gezitsn in a foredikn bunker,

00:13:22.549 --> 00:13:28.268
un der hot zikh ge- nokh vayter ⟨gelondzhet⟩, un m'makht zikh arayn in a tsveytn untererdishn bunker,

00:13:28.341 --> 00:13:36.030
get men a kuk, nares! militer, azoy vi militer. shtokn, azelkhe, eyn bet oyfn tsveytn.

00:13:36.154 --> 00:13:39.762
oyfgegrobn, aleyn gearbet bay dem bunker, oyfgegrobn azelkhe nares.

00:13:39.762 --> 00:13:44.316
host nokh gehat aroysgenumen fun shtub aroys epes untertsuleygn zikh, tsutsudekn zikh.

00:13:45.098 --> 00:13:48.740
un di khevre zenen geven, az undz zenen mir arayn in der bunker arayn,

00:13:48.740 --> 00:13:50.627
iz shoyn nisht geven keyn eyn lebediker.

00:13:50.953 --> 00:13:56.679
di doytshn hobn arayngelozt gaz. zey hobn oysgefunen, zey hobn moyre gehat arayntsukhapn zikh UNK, zey hobn gekrign,

00:13:56.679 --> 00:13:58.845
m'hot zey hobn gevust az m'hot gever bay zikh.

00:13:58.969 --> 00:14:02.847
a- moyre gehat, zey hobn ge- oysgefunen a mitl arayntsulozn

00:14:02.847 --> 00:14:06.905
gaz arayn, arayntsulozn gaz. UNK hobn gezen di mentshn vos zenen gelign in dem

00:14:06.905 --> 00:14:11.889
bunker zenen zey geven halb geshvoln fun dem gaz, o- azoy zenen geven di baykher.

00:14:12.216 --> 00:14:17.444
un dortn in dem bunker, ot bay undz iz geven a toyter azoy vi oystsutrinken a vaser.

00:14:17.444 --> 00:14:19.443
tsu kukn vi mentshn shtarbn

00:14:19.443 --> 00:14:24.970
iz bay mir geven un bay andere mentshn geven azoy vi oystsutrinken, vayl m'iz geven tsugevoynt tsu di meysim.

00:14:24.970 --> 00:14:29.827
tsu di geshiseray, tsu di brokhen, tsu di un bay brenen, azoy az ikh hob ikh hob gornisht.

00:14:29.867 --> 00:14:37.235
ikh hob gekukt vi zey lign ale vi geshvoln, un a sakh mentshn geven un toyt, ale toyt, ikh bin tsugeganen.

00:14:33.665 --> 00:14:35.435
vifl mentshn?

00:14:37.427 --> 00:14:41.052
iz m- hobn zey arayngenumen tsu zikh oykhet esn,

00:14:41.052 --> 00:14:45.465
hobn hot men gekrign fun oysern geto, hot men opgekoyft a militerishe

00:14:45.465 --> 00:14:50.718
azelkhe TINS mit fleysh, hermetish farmakht vos dos ken nisht kalye vern.

00:14:50.978 --> 00:14:55.933
vayl dos iz alts gekoyft gevorn fun shmuglers arayn in geto, undz hobn nisht geha- s'shoyn geven militerishe.

00:14:55.990 --> 00:15:00.551
farshteyst, un m'hot dos, un ikh hob aroysgenumen di, ikh mit nokh vemen, aroysgenumen pushkes,

00:15:00.551 --> 00:15:02.154
m'hot es aroyfgenumen in der UNK,

00:15:02.154 --> 00:15:08.724
m'hot oyfgeefnt di pushkes, m'hot gegesn fleysh koydem. vaser hot men gehat fun dem mikve, hot men zikh shoyn gekent a bisl dernern.

00:15:08.899 --> 00:15:12.640
iz geven geferlekh, s'geven shlekht, ober s'nisht geven an eytse, shoyn.

00:15:12.640 --> 00:15:14.681
m'iz opgeven dort a sheyne por vokhn.

00:15:15.295 --> 00:15:16.588
shtel dikh for,

00:15:16.273 --> 00:15:17.279
vokhn?!

00:15:17.337 --> 00:15:20.334
vokh- vart unter! far vos vokhn?

00:15:20.762 --> 00:15:23.371
ikh bin gekhapt gevorn ersht in tsvelftn may.

00:15:24.002 --> 00:15:28.040
fun nayntstn bin ikh heyst dokh UNK, april,

00:15:26.398 --> 00:15:27.590
april.

00:15:28.040 --> 00:15:30.223
bizn tsvelftn may iz a por vokhn.

00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:37.142
der kamf iz ongegangen, nor loyt vi s'vert bashribn az s'gevorn az s'geven a por monatn,

00:15:37.249 --> 00:15:41.377
ikh hob gehert az s'bashribn az der kamf in geto iz ongegangen a por monatn.

00:15:41.586 --> 00:15:45.118
s'iz a bisl ibergetribn, ober s'geven a kamf.

00:15:45.118 --> 00:15:50.118
koydem hot men nokh oysgefunen a sakh mentshn fun baheltenishn aroysgeshlept

00:15:50.378 --> 00:15:53.361
un geshosn, dos iz geven farbrekhers.

00:15:53.361 --> 00:15:56.463
yidn vos m'hot gekhapt, yeder mentsh iz geven an oyfshtender.

00:15:56.571 --> 00:15:59.521
vayl zey hobn gehat aza mapole az zey hobn nisht gekent shoyn kukn

00:15:59.521 --> 00:16:01.714
az zey hobn im bald gegebn im a por koyln.

00:16:01.714 --> 00:16:04.597
yedern mentsh vos er vert gekhapt iz geshosn gevorn.

00:16:04.857 --> 00:16:07.933
m'hot gehert in der heykh zitsndik oyf dem UNK oyf di shtign,

00:16:07.933 --> 00:16:12.241
hot men geven aza shiseray, yedn tog hot men geshosn. undz zenen mir oyf der heykh gezitsn.

00:16:12.332 --> 00:16:15.397
adurkhgegangen efsher tsvey tsi dray vokhn bizn ende.

00:16:16.146 --> 00:16:22.850
kumt tsu di tsayt tsi tsi dem may, iz oyfn hoyf geyen arum,

00:16:22.850 --> 00:16:29.639
yo, iz eyner aropgegangen fun undz iz eyner aropgegangen, er takesht er der Teytlboym

00:16:29.646 --> 00:16:31.727
iz aropgegangen, er hot zikh tsugedekt

00:16:31.727 --> 00:16:35.566
mit a shtik blekh, veyst vos blekh iz, di UNK, veyst vos blekh,

00:16:34.287 --> 00:16:37.217
mm, mm, yo, yo yo, yo.

00:16:35.566 --> 00:16:36.947
m'fardekt blekher.

00:16:37.138 --> 00:16:40.805
iz geven a shtik blekh, un di blekh iz geven adurkhgehakt mit mashin gever.

00:16:40.805 --> 00:16:42.484
iz geven zeyer a sakh lekher,

00:16:42.484 --> 00:16:47.572
un er hot gevolt tsu kukn tsi di doytshn geyen shoyn arayn, vayl zey zenen dokh gegangen azoy fil

00:16:47.572 --> 00:16:50.412
hayzer un azoy fil hayfer, tsi zey zenen shoyn bay undz do.

00:16:50.723 --> 00:16:55.183
shoyn az m- vos iz? hot er undz gegebn a bafel m'zol zayn, keyn eyn vort nisht redn,

00:16:55.183 --> 00:16:59.300
iz UNK gumene shtivl zey geyen mit, un yeder vort ebn zey khapn,

00:16:59.300 --> 00:17:02.091
az m'zol nisht UNK emetser redn tsu zey keyn eyn vort.

00:17:02.940 --> 00:17:08.232
dervayl hot men gehert a kol, a yidish kol.

00:17:09.319 --> 00:17:13.228
az yidn gets enk unter, m'veyst zenen dortn do,

00:17:13.487 --> 00:17:17.598
her oys, ikh ken nisht bashuldikn dem yid, hots nisht keyn UNK, m'hot im tsugezogt azoy.

00:17:17.622 --> 00:17:21.787
ts- un du vest lebn, di m- un efsher di vos m'hot gekhapt di froy,

00:17:21.787 --> 00:17:25.682
hot hot im m'hot im gegebn tsu esn. iz er arayngekumen bay der nakht,

00:17:25.738 --> 00:17:29.461
ven di yidn khapn zikh aroys fun di kelern, a bisl otem tsu khapn,

00:17:29.653 --> 00:17:34.540
hot er bamerkt di lekher, un er hot bamerkt undzer baheltenish in der heykh.

00:17:34.851 --> 00:17:38.307
shoyn, hot er ibergegebn, iz geven azoy. iz geven a sakh S.S. layt,

00:17:38.307 --> 00:17:42.466
un s'geven di ukrainer zenen geven, zey hobn dokh mitgearbet mit di doytshn,

00:17:42.466 --> 00:17:46.370
in zeyere shvartse mundirn mit dem shifele di shvartse.

00:17:46.630 --> 00:17:51.141
un un zey hobn ongehoybn tsu hakn mit mashin-gever tsu undzere, vi nokh geven geblibn shteyn

00:17:51.141 --> 00:17:55.401
azelkhe shtiklekh vent vos iz gevorn farbrent vos iz nisht umgefaln,

00:17:55.401 --> 00:17:59.932
hot men nokh di hot men nokh di vent gekent zikh oysbahaltn fun di koyln,

00:17:59.932 --> 00:18:05.366
nor s'hot zikh adurkhgerisn koyln, s'hot getrofn eyne, a t- a tokhter fun a mame,

00:18:05.366 --> 00:18:08.966
shoyn eltere, s'nisht keyn eltere, ikh veys, a etlekhe tsvontsik yor a meydl,

00:18:09.073 --> 00:18:12.419
farshteyst, hobn ir ir getrofn a koyl, nisht in harts arayn, nor a b-

00:18:12.419 --> 00:18:17.876
do in di di zaytn fun dem fun di eybershte teyl hot zi gekrign a koyl, un s'hot zikh gegosn dos blut,

00:18:17.882 --> 00:18:20.525
rateven hot men nisht gekent, eng zenen mir gezitsn,

00:18:20.565 --> 00:18:24.491
iz geven zeyer shver. un z- un m'hot nisht nokhgegebn, m'hot zikh nisht untergegebn.

00:18:24.649 --> 00:18:28.440
hobn zey gekrign a bafel m'zol aroyfshikn an ukrainers in der heykh aroyf,

00:18:29.256 --> 00:18:32.577
zey hobn ge- un gekent doytshn, zey hobn zikh oysgelernt gut di banditn.

00:18:32.577 --> 00:18:35.088
zenen nokh geven erger vi di doytshn, di ukrainer.

00:18:35.415 --> 00:18:39.374
du farshteyst? un der khevre man gey- m'hot geheysn zol zikh aroyf raybn

00:18:39.415 --> 00:18:41.147
dortn aroyf, s'geven azelkhe

00:18:41.254 --> 00:18:48.001
ayzerne, m'hot gekent zikh aroyfkhapn, vayl undz zenen mir nokh arop nokh far zey, far m- mener, UNK yunge mener geven mir geven feik

00:18:48.001 --> 00:18:49.905
tsu shlepn arop vaser aroptsugeyn.

00:18:50.502 --> 00:18:54.641
iz der khevre man iz tsugegangen tsu dem baheltenish ven undz zenen mir geven, tsu dem hoyz,

00:18:54.641 --> 00:19:01.079
farbrentn, un nisht vilndik hot er avek geshtupt di shtik blekh, s'hot im geshtert aroystsugeyn,

00:19:01.079 --> 00:19:05.311
get er a kuk der der khevre man ligt, a JUDE!

00:19:05.858 --> 00:19:11.539
shoyn, er vayter vayzt undz aroyf mit der hant, m'iz ale m'iz ale,

00:19:12.928 --> 00:19:18.249
un er hot zikh aroyfgekhapt UNK, undz hobn nisht gevolt aropgeyn, UNK di froyen iz geven ummeglekh aroptsulozn zikh

00:19:18.249 --> 00:19:21.410
fun dray shtok, tsi fun fir shtok, fir shtok shtign,

00:19:21.838 --> 00:19:24.999
iz geven ummeglekh. un der khevre man hot zikh aroyfgekhapt in der heykh,

00:19:24.999 --> 00:19:28.652
hot di mame gebetn, gedenk ikh, az m'zol tsu shisn di tokhter,

00:19:28.652 --> 00:19:31.164
vayl vi vet zi aropgeyn, s'gist zikh dos blut?

00:19:31.356 --> 00:19:36.179
zi vil zikh nisht mordeven, hot er aropgeshrign tsu zey, zey hobn geheysn im

00:19:36.179 --> 00:19:42.116
aropnemen undz lebedikerheyt, nisht shisn gornisht. du geyst aroyf zolstu nisht shisn, m'zol zikh ale aroplozn.

00:19:42.595 --> 00:19:47.240
aroyfgekumen, hot er gefregt zey fun der heykh hintn arop tsi er ken tsu shisn,

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:52.545
s'do eyne a shver renirte, un er hot ir tsu geshisn. shtel dir for di mame mit ir gevalt!

00:19:53.749 --> 00:19:57.163
un m'hot ongehoybn undz tsu arop tsuyogn, di ukrainers,

00:19:57.163 --> 00:19:58.808
m'hot zikh ongehoybn aroptsulozn.

00:19:58.808 --> 00:20:03.952
tsun ersht mener, froyen zenen geven di letst, efsher khapt men zey, efsher ken men zey helfn.

00:20:04.347 --> 00:20:09.048
kurts geredt, m'hot undz a- oysgeshtelt in a reye,

00:20:10.152 --> 00:20:16.069
dos kenst zikh forshteln az keyn eyn mentsh vos m'hot gekhapt zol blaybn lebn.

00:20:16.497 --> 00:20:21.299
dos iz geven a nes, vest bald hern vi azoy m'hot mikh gelozt lebn.

00:20:22.032 --> 00:20:26.838
geyt men undz tsufirn tsu der vant un oysshisn UNK, keyn shum povstanyes,

00:20:26.838 --> 00:20:33.568
keyn shum oyfshtender hot nisht gekent adurkhmakhn az er zol nisht vern geshosn, vayl m'hot gehert a fayer a gantsn tog.

00:20:33.945 --> 00:20:38.259
farshteyst, hot men undz aroysgeshtelt, un m'heyst undz firn, geyn.

00:20:39.514 --> 00:20:42.748
m'hot nisht gevust vu, ober ikh gleyb m'geyt undz shisn.

00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:49.886
geven ober der der vild, neyn nisht der vild, dos moyre fun shisn, fun toyt, yunge mentshn.

00:20:51.006 --> 00:20:55.390
farshteyst, firt men undz tsu aroys oyf Frantshishkaane gas, Frantshishkane hot zikh ge-

00:20:55.390 --> 00:21:00.585
hot zikh fareynikt mit a gas, hot zi geheysn Nalefki, vu der Brauer hot gehat dem ⟨verkshtand⟩,

00:21:00.692 --> 00:21:05.928
un m'geyt tsu, er firt undz tsu tsum UNK, m'kumt tsu tsum UNK iz geven a kleyne SQUARE,

00:21:05.928 --> 00:21:15.148
veystu beymelekh, mit, a kleyne, un geb a kuk, der SQUARE is ful mit mentshn, elegant ongetun, yidn.

00:21:15.947 --> 00:21:17.611
vos iz geven mit di yidn?

00:21:18.023 --> 00:21:23.838
di polyakn hobn m'hot zey geheysn, m'hot zey batsolt, zoln oysgebn,

00:21:24.013 --> 00:21:27.444
vayl s'geven mentshn, yidn, velkhe zey hobn ge- oysgearbet zikh

00:21:27.444 --> 00:21:32.124
ken-kartn, mit a poylishn nomen, zenen polyakn,

00:21:32.333 --> 00:21:37.324
batsolt sheyn, un di polyakn hobn ⟨mimeyle gedorfn⟩ m'zol aroyskrign fun di yidn a bisl gelt,

00:21:37.324 --> 00:21:41.827
m'hot oysgearbet, in di amtn vu zey zenen geven hot men oysgearbet, s'hot nisht geshpilt a role.

00:21:41.884 --> 00:21:47.534
farshteyst, un un di polyakn un der doytsh hot gezen a ken-karte, er hot gezen az er iz nisht keyn JUDE hot er im avekgelozt.

00:21:47.534 --> 00:21:51.651
hot der polyak im ongevizn un m'hot zey ale arayngehakt in dem SQUARE arayn,

00:21:51.651 --> 00:21:58.364
geven a groyse grupe mentshn ongetun zikh, vayl zey hobn gevolt vayzn az zey zenen polyakn ongetun, az m'zol nisht derkenen az zey zenen yidn,

00:21:59.586 --> 00:22:05.750
un m'hot dos iz geven undzer mazl, m'hot undz nisht geshosn, ven undz zenen mir bloyz di kleyntshike grupe volt men undz oysgeshosn.

00:22:05.750 --> 00:22:10.129
geven a groyse grupe mentshn, hobn zey undz tsugevorfn tsu di grupe,

00:22:10.129 --> 00:22:15.813
un m'hot undz oysgeshtelt m'zol onheybn loyfn. un loyfn fun rikhtung fun umshlag-plats.

00:22:16.090 --> 00:22:18.837
demolt iz shoyn nisht geven keyn eyn hoyz keyn gants.

00:22:18.837 --> 00:22:25.216
far vos? vayl loyfedikerheyt, ven m'iz gelofn, iz geven groys shtikl vegs.

00:22:25.216 --> 00:22:27.908
fun dem Frantshishkane arop Nalefki iz geven

00:22:27.908 --> 00:22:32.182
a groys shtik veg tsum umshlag, umshlag iz geven oyf Stafke gas, zeyer a groyse shtik veg.

00:22:32.610 --> 00:22:35.011
loyfndikerheyt hot men arumgekukt zikh

00:22:35.011 --> 00:22:39.129
vu m'hot nisht gehat in kop tsu geyn, m'hot nisht vilndik iz men ariber mit di khurves,

00:22:39.129 --> 00:22:44.079
m'hot undz genumen tsvishn di shteyner un di di ayngefalene vayl zey hobn tsum ersht mit harmatn gehakt.

00:22:44.102 --> 00:22:46.813
zey hobn tsehakt, dernokh iz shoyn geven farbrente hayzer.

00:22:46.836 --> 00:22:52.047
ikh vil eyn vort zogn az s'farblibn a simbol, hobn zey ibergelozt eyn hoyz,

00:22:52.047 --> 00:22:58.608
fun gantsn groysn geto, du host a bagrif vifl hayzer dortn geven in dem yidishn geto, in dem geto.

00:22:59.053 --> 00:23:05.243
azoy zey hobn ibergelozt oyf dos iz geven oyf Moranovski gas, nisht Moranovski, Plats Moranovski hot es geheysn,

00:23:05.243 --> 00:23:17.073
un dortn eyn hoyz hobn zey ibergelozt. dos hob ikh gezen ven ikh bin bafrayt gevorn shoyn bin ikh arayn in Varshe in dem zen in in di khurves, hob ikh gevolt, s'hot mikh getsoygn tsu gebn a kuk vi azoy s'hot oysgezen der kamf dort,

00:23:17.073 --> 00:23:24.562
di khurves, ikh hob gevolt gefinen mayn ho- hoyf, mayne ge- vu ikh hob a mol gevoynt, s'hot mir epes getsoygn,

00:23:24.737 --> 00:23:29.130
un ikh hob bamerkt oyf der Plats Moranovski shteyt eyn hoyz a gants,

00:23:29.130 --> 00:23:32.207
efsher ibergelozt far a simbol tsi vos, dos veys ikh nisht.

00:23:32.922 --> 00:23:38.200
du farshteyst, zenen kurts geredt m'hot undz geyogt ahin tsum umshlag-plats, m'hot undz arayn,

00:23:38.200 --> 00:23:42.686
barn umshlag iz geven a groyse BUILDING dort, hobn men tsunoyfgenumen zeyer a sakh mentshn,

00:23:42.692 --> 00:23:45.127
zeyer nokh fun friert zey zenen zey gezitsn,

00:23:45.127 --> 00:23:50.190
vayl zey hobn gevolt onkloybn a groysn transport, vayl der ban zol nisht geyn leydik mit eyn vagon,

00:23:50.190 --> 00:23:56.771
azoy az m'hot ongehoybn, iz m'iz gezitsn tsvey tog, kloybn nokh efsher mentshn, nokh gefunene mentshn,

00:23:56.771 --> 00:24:02.041
s'geven zeyer shver dortn aroystsukrikhn fun dem fayer ort, vayl zey hobn geharget mentshn bald oyfn ort.

00:24:02.115 --> 00:24:04.674
nor s'geven mentshn fun frierte zeyer a sakh.

00:24:05.018 --> 00:24:09.450
un di vagonen zenen shoyn geshtanen, farmakhte vagonen, azoy vi far di beheymes,

00:24:09.962 --> 00:24:15.097
un m'hot ongehoybn aroystsushikn di mentshn fun dem groysn BUILDING aroys,

00:24:15.097 --> 00:24:19.879
un m'hot undz arayngevorfn in di vagonen arayn, geven a gepakter vagon,

00:24:19.513 --> 00:24:22.139
vifl mentshn in a vagon?

00:24:20.560 --> 00:24:24.691
o s'hot gekent arayn ikh veys geven ikh veys, azoy az er iz geven,

00:24:24.691 --> 00:24:28.277
optseyln vifl mentshn hot men gekent, nor er iz geven gepakt.

00:24:28.277 --> 00:24:34.638
kenst zikh forshteln in a in a groysn vagon vu ferd, beheymes, ki firt men, vi groys er iz.

00:24:34.638 --> 00:24:36.787
yederer vagon hot gehat zikh

00:24:36.810 --> 00:24:46.187
azelkhe fir fentsterlekh, yeder ek iz geven a fentsterl, undz zenen mir geven zeyer geprest, zey hobn nokh tsugeshtupt mitn fus m'zol kenen farmakhn di tir, farhakn di tir,

00:24:46.210 --> 00:24:49.742
un un iz geven fir fentsterlekh in dem vagon,

00:24:49.742 --> 00:24:52.661
un bay yeder fentster, dos iz shoyn geven azoy shtreng demolt,

00:24:52.661 --> 00:24:55.707
vayl s'geven frierter iz men nokh aroys durkh a fentsterl,

00:24:55.707 --> 00:24:58.441
ven dos ven der ban iz geblibn shteyn bin ikh dertlofn,

00:24:58.441 --> 00:25:01.833
nor zey hobn gevust fun di ale zakhn, m'dertloyft, m'ratevet zikh,

00:25:01.833 --> 00:25:03.874
nisht mer, bay undz iz shoyn dos nisht geven.

00:25:03.874 --> 00:25:08.073
bay yedern fetsterl iz gezitsn an S.S. man, mit mashin-gever.

00:25:09.025 --> 00:25:15.971
ven m'hot undz arayngepakt un m'iz adurkhgeforn a gevisn gegnt, hot men gevust az m'fort keyn Treblinke.

00:25:17.260 --> 00:25:21.045
Treblinke dos iz toyt. dos iz geven dort iz nisht s'nisht keyn arbet-lager,

00:25:21.045 --> 00:25:24.662
s'iz gornisht, dort geyt men in di gaz-kamern, dos hobn mir gevust genoy.

00:25:24.988 --> 00:25:28.782
farshteyst, Treblinke hot zikh ongehoybn dortn a mehume in dem vagon.

00:25:28.782 --> 00:25:35.343
dos ersht di froyen, m'hot ongehoybn tsu shrayen, ⟨tsi dorfn⟩ zey di mener arumkhapn zey, nu m'geyt fargazevet vern.

00:25:35.721 --> 00:25:38.297
fargazevet vern iz nisht fun di laykhtste zakhn.

00:25:39.096 --> 00:25:42.999
un azoy hobn zey gehert di geshreyen un di gevaltn,

00:25:42.999 --> 00:25:48.475
hot er genumen di mashin, dem fentsterl, arayngeshtelt di mashin-gever, un arayngehakt a serye koyln.

00:25:48.475 --> 00:25:51.715
a sakh mentshn vos zenen geven noent tsum fentster hobn gekrign di koyln.

00:25:51.715 --> 00:25:54.611
iz geven fun andern fentster oykh dos zelbe, azoy s'iz geven,

00:25:54.641 --> 00:25:56.789
ikh bin tsufelik, nisht far derfar vayl

00:25:56.789 --> 00:26:01.437
efsher iz dos geven nisim, geven in mitn vagon, ikh bin nisht geven noent der fentster mit der froy.

00:26:01.443 --> 00:26:04.722
un zi iz oykhet geven mit gevaltn mit mit geshreyen,

00:26:06.298 --> 00:26:08.961
iz yo, iz shoyn geven, iz geshtanen a mase

00:26:08.961 --> 00:26:14.505
a mase mentshn, nisht umfaln, az m'krigt di koyl ken men nisht umfaln, vayl m- m'iz geven geprest.

00:26:14.505 --> 00:26:20.023
un iz geven a sakh ranirte, s'geven afilek toyte gehargete, ikh hob es nisht gekent

00:26:20.023 --> 00:26:26.761
bamerkn ver s'iz toyt un ver s'bamerkt, bin ikh bin geshtanen in mayne tsores, un geprest

00:26:26.785 --> 00:26:31.954
shoyn m'iz geforn avek a lengere tsayt, ⟨ukreshne⟩ vi ven, vi lang s'hot gedoyert

00:26:31.954 --> 00:26:36.937
dos forn, vayl zey shteln zikh op, di tseger shteln zikh op, m'lozt adurkh pasazhir

00:26:36.960 --> 00:26:41.445
militerishe tseger, shtelt men zey avek oyf an andern peron,

00:26:41.445 --> 00:26:46.877
un un m'vart iber biz a tsug geyt adurkh, hot geven a lengere tsayt shlepn zikh dortn ahin,

00:26:46.536 --> 00:26:48.227
shoen o teg?

00:26:48.047 --> 00:26:54.369
o neyn, keyn teg nisht, teg nisht. ikh bin in zelbn tog ongekumen dort. farshteyst, az,

00:26:53.329 --> 00:26:56.665
ven bistu avek fun Varshe?

00:26:56.923 --> 00:26:59.786
ven ikh bin avek in, veyst dokh, in velkhe DATE?

00:26:57.615 --> 00:27:02.706
in der f- in neyn, in tog, iz geven in der fri, nokh mitog?

00:27:01.800 --> 00:27:06.513
neyn, dos iz ge- ikh gleyb nisht, ikh ken efsher tsuriktsien, efsher iz nisht geven keyn tog.

00:27:06.513 --> 00:27:09.922
ikh ken nisht genoy visn s'nisht geven, vayl undz zenen mir geven in vagon

00:27:09.922 --> 00:27:13.837
in azelkhe tsores, ikh hob nisht gekent trakhtn, on vaser, on gornisht.

00:27:13.837 --> 00:27:19.580
ken a mol zayn efsher lenger afile vi a tog, vayl undz hot men gekhapt in der fri, efsher iz es geven in zelbn tog.

00:27:20.481 --> 00:27:22.854
azoy az genoy ken ikh dir ken ikh dir nisht zogn.

00:27:24.058 --> 00:27:31.969
iz azoy, iz tsukumendik, m'iz gekumen, yo m'hot a- m'iz adurkhgeforn a shtetl, Volomnyen m'hot gevust der gegnt geyt epes dortn ahin,

00:27:31.969 --> 00:27:34.093
demolts hot zikh ongehoybn di khasene in vagon.

00:27:34.572 --> 00:27:38.835
shoyn m'iz dortn ahingekumen in dem in dem Treblinke,

00:27:38.841 --> 00:27:44.589
veyst dokh barn oyslodn di mentshn, hot men gegebn an efn oyf di vagonen, iz aroysgefaln a mase

00:27:44.595 --> 00:27:48.369
a mase gepreste mentshn, lebedike, in ⟨yit⟩ toyte.

00:27:48.392 --> 00:27:50.293
nisht geven vemen tsu redn un shoyn.

00:27:50.670 --> 00:27:55.659
un ikh bin geven eyner fun di lebedike mit der froy, vayl ikh bin geven in mitn dem vagon,

00:27:56.070 --> 00:28:00.620
un s'iz, yo, m'heyst ale oyfshteyn, di vos zey lebn farshteyt zikh,

00:28:01.099 --> 00:28:08.855
un dreyt arum ze ikh vi s'geyen arum yidn vos zey trogn azelkhe BLANKETS,

00:28:09.013 --> 00:28:11.440
eyner in di zayt, eyner in di andere zayt,

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:15.676
ver s'hot zikh, zey hobn gevust az yidn hobn ale mol bay zikh a bisl gold, a bisl bahaltene,

00:28:15.676 --> 00:28:20.013
efsher vet er iberlebn, efsher vet UNK blaybn, azoy iz geven aynge-

00:28:20.013 --> 00:28:22.305
m'hot shoyn gevust, yederer zol hobn epes gold.

00:28:23.037 --> 00:28:30.045
un a bisl hot men genumen fun di shtubn, fun di vilde shtubn aroyf vos m'hot aropgenumen di mentshn, iz oykhet ibergeblibn a bisl tsirung,

00:28:30.045 --> 00:28:35.900
azoy az m'hot, az zey hobn geheysn, ver s'hot nor epes fun fun di zakhn, ⟨vartsuh-⟩ heyst es e-

00:28:35.900 --> 00:28:39.157
⟨yubleye⟩ zakhn, andere, araynvarfn in di kotsn arayn.

00:28:39.157 --> 00:28:44.810
iz geven tsvey azelkhe kotsn-treger, vos zey hobn getrogn di BLANKETn, zey hobn gedos.

00:28:44.810 --> 00:28:56.441
tsvishn andere iz geven a bakanter mayner, vos er iz gevorn gekhapt oykhet in geto, m'hot arayngefirt keyn Treblinke, un zey hobn oysgeklibn mentshn velkhe zenen nokh feik tsu arbetn vos ebn kenen

00:28:56.547 --> 00:29:01.845
ineveynik arbetn, barn gaz arbetn, aroysnemen di toyte tsu dem oyvn tsu farbrenen,

00:29:01.845 --> 00:29:03.716
hot men badorfn hobn mentshn,

00:29:03.925 --> 00:29:06.889
un zey, un er iz geven eyner fun zey. freg ikh im,

00:29:06.895 --> 00:29:12.122
vi azoy zet oys do, tsi m- s'do epes a shans a CHANCE

00:29:12.122 --> 00:29:14.752
ibertsulebn do in dem gehenem? zogt er,

00:29:14.826 --> 00:29:19.540
keyn CHANCE iz nishto do, do geyen al- direkt geyt dos in dem

00:29:19.540 --> 00:29:24.793
bod arayn, s'do azelkhe di SHOWERS vos m'hot gemakht, vos der kerper hot gemuzt vern heys,

00:29:25.103 --> 00:29:31.065
un nor vos iz, s'do a shans, oyb vest zayn eyner fun di gliklekhste

00:29:31.065 --> 00:29:38.799
iz do a shans, s'iz do a telefon fun fun Maydanek, dos iz lebn Lublin a groyse kontsentratsye lager,

00:29:38.805 --> 00:29:41.128
mit di gaz-kamers dort ayngeordnt.

00:29:41.202 --> 00:29:48.941
az du vest vern oysgeklibn arayn in oyf tsurik tsu vu Maydanek, vestu, bay do geystu direkt geharget tsu vern.

00:29:49.369 --> 00:29:53.323
shoyn, shtelt men aroys a reye, m'yogt, zey hobn nisht ge- gegangen,

00:29:53.323 --> 00:29:57.440
di froyen hobn zey oykhet geyogt mit beyde zaytn mit di vi nokh heysn zey di sh-

00:29:57.440 --> 00:30:02.646
gehakt arayn, kedey az a mentsh zol zikh nisht oryentirn az er loyft tsu az er loyft tsum toyt.

00:30:02.646 --> 00:30:06.913
hobn zey azoy tsemisht dem mentsh az m'hot shoyn gevolt patern dos lebn.

00:30:06.970 --> 00:30:11.177
farshteyst, un undz hobn mir gekrign di zelbe mayse, m'hot undz gehakt gehakt, m'iz gelofn,

00:30:11.177 --> 00:30:16.332
m'iz tsugekumen tsu dem tsu dem tsu di SHOWERS, tsu dem arayngang tsu di SHOWERS, hobn a sakh mentshn,

00:30:16.332 --> 00:30:22.264
neyn, iz geshtanen S.S., un m'hot oysgeklibn mentshn, m'hot nisht gevust vos far a toyt m'geyt undz gebn,

00:30:22.264 --> 00:30:24.930
ikh bin geven fun eynem vos hot mikh geheysn,

00:30:24.930 --> 00:30:29.975
hot gegebn veyst dokh a zets mit di nagaye, az ikh zol mikh dortn hin leygn, avekleygn zikh dos heyst.

00:30:29.975 --> 00:30:34.515
un ikh kum dort oyf a vayt ort, nisht vayt nisht noent azoy tsu di gaz-kamer.

00:30:34.515 --> 00:30:39.313
dort UNK, geb ikh a kum tsu tsu dem ort, ze ikh vi s'ligt shoyn a groyse grupe yidn.

00:30:39.387 --> 00:30:42.148
oysgeklibene, barn oyvn hot men zey oysgeklibn.

00:30:43.065 --> 00:30:47.677
mir hot men nisht geheysn oystun ven m'hot mir oysgeklibn. di ale mentshn hot men geheysn oystun zikh naket,

00:30:47.677 --> 00:30:50.925
vayl m'ken dokh nisht arayngeyn in keyn SHOWER arayn. zey hobn mir bite gezogt

00:30:50.925 --> 00:30:53.297
az m'geyt arayn zikh oysbodn

00:30:53.297 --> 00:30:58.635
m- nokhn geyn tsu der arbet, zey hobn opgenart. ober s'hot nisht geholfn, mentshn hobn gevust az m'geyt tsum toyt.

00:30:58.692 --> 00:31:03.354
dos iz geven a SHOWER velkhe zeyer a sakh SHOWERS in eyn groysn bod.

00:31:03.354 --> 00:31:08.051
zeyer a sakh, vayl m'hot arayngelozt a sheyn bisl mentshn, vifl der gaz-kamer hot gekent farnemen.

00:31:08.074 --> 00:31:11.336
un m'hot gelozt di heyse SHOWERS un der kerper hot ongehoybn

00:31:11.336 --> 00:31:15.673
tsu tsush- tsu di pare iz aroysgegangen fun di kerper aroys,

00:31:15.673 --> 00:31:21.888
hot der gaz, der Tsayklon, ongehoybn tsu arbetn. er hot gekent samen di mentshn.

00:31:22.013 --> 00:31:27.643
vayl trukene mentshn on va- on a pare iz a bisl shver s'zol onheybn arbetn.

00:31:27.750 --> 00:31:33.262
in dem gaz-kamer iz geven in der heykh a a efenung, harmetish farmakht,

00:31:33.572 --> 00:31:37.163
zey hobn oyfgeefnt dos, ven der b- ven der bod iz geven ful,

00:31:37.163 --> 00:31:41.998
hot men, ven m'hot zey arayngelozt in der anderer, s'geven an ander opteylung, ikh gedenk ven ikh nokh di krig

00:31:41.998 --> 00:31:46.622
bin ikh geven in azan bod un ikh bin geven in Maydanek in dem gaz-kamer bin ikh geven.

00:31:46.622 --> 00:31:49.546
bald in zelbe kurts far di nokh di krig.

00:31:49.671 --> 00:31:52.635
azoy az ikh veys in zey vi nokh dortn hot oysgezen, farshteyst.

00:31:53.839 --> 00:31:59.739
OK m'adurkh hakn do, WE'LL END TAPE FOUR,

00:31:58.935 --> 00:31:59.851
vyole.

00:32:01.438 --> 00:32:02.122
THANK YOU.
